## 🔍 Port Scan Detection (Project 2)

```spl
-- Detect multiple port connections from one IP
index=lab_logs
| stats dc(dest_port) as unique_ports by src_ip
| where unique_ports > 10
| sort -unique_ports

-- Find SYN scan activity
index=lab_logs tcp_flag=SYN
| stats count by src_ip
| where count > 100

-- Detect rapid sequential port access
index=lab_logs
| bin _time span=1m
| stats dc(dest_port) as ports_per_min by _time, src_ip
| where ports_per_min > 20
```

