## 🐚 Reverse Shell Detection (Project 3)

```spl
-- Detect unusual outbound connections
index=lab_logs dest_port!=80 dest_port!=443
| stats count by src_ip, dest_ip, dest_port
| sort -count

-- Find netcat connections
index=lab_logs "nc" OR "netcat" OR "/bin/sh" OR "/bin/bash"
| table _time, src_ip, dest_ip, dest_port, _raw

-- Detect suspicious outbound ports
index=lab_logs dest_port IN (4444, 1234, 9999, 6666, 7777)
| table _time, src_ip, dest_ip, dest_port
```

