## 🌐 Web Attack Detection (Project 8)

```spl
-- SQL injection attempts
index=lab_logs ("SELECT" OR "UNION" OR "DROP" OR "INSERT" OR "1=1")
| table _time, src_ip, uri, status

-- XSS attempts
index=lab_logs ("<script>" OR "javascript:" OR "onerror=")
| table _time, src_ip, uri

-- HTTP error spike (possible scanning)
index=lab_logs status=404
| timechart span=1m count by src_ip
| where count > 20

-- Encoded payloads in URL
index=lab_logs uri="*%3C*" OR uri="*%27*" OR uri="*%22*"
| table _time, src_ip, uri, status
```

