## 📡 Beaconing Detection (Project 6)

```spl
-- Detect regular interval connections (C2 beaconing)
index=lab_logs
| bin _time span=1m
| stats count by _time, src_ip, dest_ip
| streamstats avg(count) as avg_count by src_ip, dest_ip
| eval deviation=abs(count-avg_count)
| where deviation < 2

-- Find connections at regular intervals
index=lab_logs
| stats count by src_ip, dest_ip
| where count > 50
```

