## 📈 Time-Based Searches

```spl
earliest=-15m                 ← Last 15 minutes
earliest=-1h                  ← Last 1 hour
earliest=-24h                 ← Last 24 hours
earliest=-7d                  ← Last 7 days
earliest=0                    ← All time

-- Example: SSH failures in last hour
index=lab_logs "Failed password" earliest=-1h
| stats count by src_ip
```

