## 📊 Useful Stats Functions

```spl
stats count by src_ip              ← Count events per IP
stats dc(dest_port) by src_ip      ← Count unique ports per IP
stats avg(count) by src_ip         ← Average count per IP
stats max(count) by src_ip         ← Maximum count per IP
stats min(count) by src_ip         ← Minimum count per IP
stats sum(bytes) by src_ip         ← Total bytes per IP
stats values(user) by src_ip       ← List unique users per IP
stats first(_time) by src_ip       ← First event time per IP
stats last(_time) by src_ip        ← Last event time per IP
```

