## 💡 SPL Tips

- Use `*` as wildcard: `"Failed*"` matches "Failed password", "Failed login" etc.
- Field names are case-sensitive: `src_ip` ≠ `Src_IP`
- Pipe `|` chains commands together — read left to right
- Always specify `index=` to speed up searches
- Use time picker to narrow results before running heavy queries
- `Ctrl+\` in search bar formats your SPL for readability
